fresh lemongrass, white part only, cut into pieces","4 fresh Kaffir lime leaves","1 tbsp peanut oil","1000 g gravy beef, cut into pieces (5 - 6 cm)","270 g canned coconut milk","1 pinch salt, to taste","20 - 30 g palm sugar, to taste"]}],"id":"r68545","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-Vn0MwgTrRoo\/XZQvteofdrI\/AAAAAAAAce0\/jGQaAGWszXQ5lpwtAtPhglSPxlWfekvYwCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_Kpz1Ve5BtYmUhrXo.png","title":"Beef rendang","publishedAt":"2014-09-05T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"53 g","fat":"38 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"11 g","calories":"2512 kJ \/ 598 kcal"},"basicInfo":["medium","10m","1h 40m","4 portions"]}